  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/afc589742bd571f63b2cb6389b5b8190.poster.avif?t=1660334660\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/afc589742bd571f63b2cb6389b5b8190.webm?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/afc589742bd571f63b2cb6389b5b8190.mp4?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sky Rogue is a fwooshy rogue-lite action flight simulator! Blow things up over land, sea, and air, on an infinite number of procedurally-generated islands. Choose one of a diverse set of aeros and kit it out with a dizzying array of weaponry. Go toe-to-toe with enemy aces or assault giant flying aircraft carriers and battleships, but watch out for volleys of missiles; when you die, you're dead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/3816f642174d60439ee4a3bc17becfbb.poster.avif?t=1660334660\" width=540 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/3816f642174d60439ee4a3bc17becfbb.webm?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/3816f642174d60439ee4a3bc17becfbb.mp4?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 player splitscreen local co-op<br></li><li>Infinite procedurally-generated missions<br></li><li>Rogue-lite gameplay paired with permanent unlocks<br></li><li>12+ pilotable aircraft, 30+ weapons, customizable loadouts<br></li><li>Secret technologies unlockable after completing the game once</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/cb952353836b7fe6153ad5df9ccdd7ce.poster.avif?t=1660334660\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/cb952353836b7fe6153ad5df9ccdd7ce.webm?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/cb952353836b7fe6153ad5df9ccdd7ce.mp4?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/afc589742bd571f63b2cb6389b5b8190.poster.avif?t=1660334660\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/afc589742bd571f63b2cb6389b5b8190.webm?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/afc589742bd571f63b2cb6389b5b8190.mp4?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Sky Rogue is a fwooshy rogue-lite action flight simulator! Blow things up over land, sea, and air, on an infinite number of procedurally-generated islands. Choose one of a diverse set of aeros and kit it out with a dizzying array of weaponry. Go toe-to-toe with enemy aces or assault giant flying aircraft carriers and battleships, but watch out for volleys of missiles; when you die, you're dead.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/3816f642174d60439ee4a3bc17becfbb.poster.avif?t=1660334660\" width=540 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/3816f642174d60439ee4a3bc17becfbb.webm?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/3816f642174d60439ee4a3bc17becfbb.mp4?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2 player splitscreen local co-op<br></li><li>Infinite procedurally-generated missions<br></li><li>Rogue-lite gameplay paired with permanent unlocks<br></li><li>12+ pilotable aircraft, 30+ weapons, customizable loadouts<br></li><li>Secret technologies unlockable after completing the game once</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/cb952353836b7fe6153ad5df9ccdd7ce.poster.avif?t=1660334660\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/cb952353836b7fe6153ad5df9ccdd7ce.webm?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/381020/extras/cb952353836b7fe6153ad5df9ccdd7ce.mp4?t=1660334660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
